y, optical, and UV during early 2017 and mid-2020 when the source was in\na very high state. A single zone SSC emission model is considered to model the\nspectral energy distributions and this helps us to explore the nature of this\nBL Lac with binary super-massive black holes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 May 2021 21:31:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
