r abundances of these isotopes could be reproduced\nby the mixture of the high- and low-$\\rho_c$ near-$M_{\\rm Ch}$ and sub-$M_{\\rm\nCh}$ Type Ia events, with $\\lesssim$ 20 % being high-$\\rho_c$ near-$M_{\\rm\nCh}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 May 2021 04:02:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-15"}
