lt of Belkhechine et al. which states that\ndeciding whether ${\\rm inv}(T)\\leq k$ for a given tournament $T$ is\npolynomial-time solvable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 May 2021 06:37:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 15:27:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 08:52:03 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 3 Dec 2022 18:49:21 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 18 Dec 2022 23:18:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-20"}
